Class Assignment

java.lang.Object
Assignment
public class Assignment
extends java.lang.Object
This class represents an assignment of a substitute teacher to an absence to be filled. Documentation for basic accessors and mutators is omitted.
Author:
Theodore Campbell, 3461781, Abdur Rahman Chowdhury, 3690692
